{"tid":1357122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗ADC(crime)游乃強份人一啲人情味都冇，對自己友都去到好撚盡。","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:27:10.000Z","uid":259055,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab7628fa31b1c45b3414860b8b30d98cbd9a267","tid":1357122,"uid":259055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"廿幾年前，游乃強加入Force頭三年守過馬鞍山警署，PSU三隊豬粒。當年佢處理過單theft case，遇著剛剛個suspect係隔離team沙展個親戚。<br />\n<br />\n沙展有一次搭lift果陣有意無意同游提過件事，純粹想知單case去到咩status，但由頭到尾要過撤控。游當時無乜反應，無警告過個沙展佢咁講會hi嘢，扮聽完就算。<br />\n<br />\n誰不知游轉個頭將件事report咗畀CI聽，屈鳩個沙展老妨。後尾件事escalate到DVC到就殺停咗，喺無錄音嘅情況下，始終係口同鼻拗。<br />\n<br />\n唔好叫我FC，呢件事喺警界應該有唔少老屎忽都聽過，信不信由你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望睇到呢個post嘅元朗做crime嘅警察小心游乃強呢個人，元朗單嘢，他日若果上頭要搵人祭旗，分分鐘會係你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb3e088c60b07f85bccc018101f3ee2e8fce1c9","tid":1357122,"uid":259055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd6d23ab3a13420f55ff7422f706982573fa3abe","tid":1357122,"uid":259055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:04:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0117c0bf371cf19c4797e84fb640a94825f40362","tid":1357122,"uid":259055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqzSkwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqzSkwW.jpg&h=46a0d46a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f6453f21ace4aa639c4c9f866d272b2d2222793","tid":1357122,"uid":259055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"話晒大家都係香港人，唔想睇住你班警犬成為有朝一日成為代罪羔羊。"},{"pid":"271c18c946ec54d0fff8fbf048ab4aadc633b37f","tid":1357122,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:09:05